---

<section class="use-cases" id="use-cases">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Built for Your Research Workflow</h2>
      <p>Whether you're coding survey responses, running thematic analysis, or delivering client projects, Codesift speeds up the process without sacrificing control.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="use-case-grid">
      <a href="/use-cases/coding-open-ended-survey-responses" class="use-case-card">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.9"/>
            <rect x="3" y="10" width="14" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.65"/>
            <rect x="3" y="16" width="10" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>AI Coding for Survey Responses</h3>
        <p>Categorize open-ended responses faster and more consistently than manual coding — without losing control of your codebook.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Learn more →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/use-cases/thematic-analysis-for-consultants" class="use-case-card">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="8" height="8" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <rect x="13" y="3" width="8" height="8" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <rect x="3" y="13" width="8" height="8" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <rect x="13" y="13" width="8" height="8" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Thematic Analysis for Consultants</h3>
        <p>Deliver coded qualitative data to clients in hours instead of days. Focus on insights, not repetitive coding work.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Learn more →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/use-cases/qualitative-survey-coding-ai" class="use-case-card">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 3L3 7v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V7l-9-4z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Qualitative Coding with AI</h3>
        <p>You define the codes, AI applies them. No black boxes, no mysterious clusters — just transparent, reproducible coding.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Learn more →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/compare/manual-vs-ai-coding" class="use-case-card">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="8" height="18" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <rect x="13" y="3" width="8" height="18" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="8" x2="8" y2="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="12" x2="8" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="8" x2="18" y2="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="12" x2="18" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Manual vs AI Coding</h3>
        <p>Understand when manual coding still makes sense, where AI excels, and how to combine both approaches effectively.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Compare approaches →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .use-cases {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .section-header {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .use-case-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .use-case-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 28px;
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .use-case-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--amber-dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--amber-mid);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: var(--amber);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .use-case-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .use-case-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .card-link {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }

  .use-case-card:hover .card-link {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .use-cases {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }

    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .section-header p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .use-case-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
